          </p>
        </article>

        <article
          class="w-[21.375rem] md:w-[22.5rem] h-40 m-2 p-7 rounded-xl shadow-md bg-white"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <Image src={check} alt="Check" />
            <h4 class="ml-2.5 text-2xl font-medium">Step 2</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2.5 text-sm leading-6 font-normal text-shadow_gray_500">
            Join a challenge, commit to a goal, and start working out.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article
          class="w-[21.375rem] md:w-[22.5rem] h-40 m-2 p-7 rounded-xl shadow-md bg-white"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <Image src={check} alt="Check" />
            <h4 class="ml-2.5 text-2xl font-medium">Step 3</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2.5 text-sm leading-6 font-normal text-shadow_gray_500">
            Earn cash rewards by completing the challenge.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[2.8125rem]">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="px-7 py-2.5 text-base font-semibold rounded-md bg-cobalt_blue_600 text-white"
        >
          Register now</a
        >
      </div>
    </section>
